## 🟡 SHOULD FIX #7: Field length/tag-count constraints not enforced

**Spec defines**:
| Field | Constraint | Current |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| `description` | max 160 chars | Not validated |
| `tags` | max 10 items | Not validated |
| `disclosure.summary` | max 200 chars | Not validated |

**Evidence**: No validation exists in `loader.ts`, `types.ts`, or any other source file.

These are soft limits per spec semantics — loading should succeed but emit warnings. No warning mechanism exists.

